To define a structured project schedule for developing a **Data-Driven Inventory Management System**, including all key phases, timelines, and team responsibilities.

---

## ðŸ“˜ **Project Title:**
**Smart Inventory Management using Machine Learning and Predictive Analytics**

---

### ðŸ§© **Phases of the Project**

| Phase No. | Phase Name                         | Duration      | Description                                                                 |
|-----------|------------------------------------|---------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| 1         | Requirement Gathering              | 1 week        | Identify system requirements, collect datasets, meet with stakeholders.     |
| 2         | Feasibility Study & Planning       | 1 week        | Analyze scope, define goals, select ML approach and tech stack.             |
| 3         | System Design                      | 1.5 weeks     | Design system architecture, data flow diagrams, and database schemas.       |
| 4         | Data Collection & Preprocessing    | 2 weeks       | Collect historical sales/customer data, clean and format it.                |
| 5         | ML Model Development               | 2.5 weeks     | Develop and train predictive models (demand forecasting, segmentation).     |
| 6         | Backend & Inventory Logic          | 2 weeks       | Build inventory handling logic and database connectivity.                   |
| 7         | Frontend / UI Design               | 1.5 weeks     | Create dashboard/UI for shopkeepers and admin.                              |
| 8         | Integration of ML & UI             | 1 week        | Integrate predictive insights into the frontend.                            |
| 9         | Testing & Debugging                | 1 week        | Perform unit and system testing, fix bugs.                                  |
| 10        | Final Report & Presentation Prep   | 1 week        | Prepare final documentation and project presentation.                       |

---

### ðŸ“Š **Total Estimated Duration:**  
**~14.5 weeks (approx. 3.5 months)**

